	rulers and to display lengths.

	* app/widgets/gimptemplateeditor.c: redone GimpTemplateEditor
	based on a dialog mockup from Jimmac and Tigert.

	* app/core/core-enums.[ch]: changed some descriptions used by the
	template editor.

